<br id="idx10">
Install (root)

```
# USER: ROOT ============
make modules_install

make install

make headers_install INSTALL_HDR_PATH=/usr

```

<br id="idx11">
Known Boot Errors

```
ata1.00: Read log 0x00 page 0x00 failed, Emask 0x1

```

<br id="idx12">
Linux Firmware
* URL: <https://git.kernel.org/pub/scm/linux/kernel/git/firmware/linux-firmware.git/>
  * E.g. open TARBALL "linux-firmware-20220509.tar.gz"
  * Go to folder "linux-firmware-20220509/"
  * Copy the missing modules into "/lib/firmware/"

```
cp -r i915/ /lib/firmware/
cp -r tigon/ /lib/firmware/
cp -r e100/ /lib/firmware/
cp -r rtl_nic/ /lib/firmware/

```



